    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed at $47,000 and represents a truly exceptional find \u2014 a car in mint condition that is as close to perfect as a used vehicle can be. The exterior is flawless: the paint retains its full, deep gloss with no scratches, chips, dents, or fading anywhere on the body. Panel gaps are tight and even, and all trim pieces, moldings, and chrome accents are intact and pristine. The interior is equally immaculate \u2014 upholstery shows no wear, cracking, or staining, all surfaces are clean and unmarked, and every control, button, and switch functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is clean, well-maintained, and runs smoothly with no unusual noises, leaks, or warning lights. All mechanical systems \u2014 brakes, suspension, steering, transmission, and cooling \u2014 are in excellent working order. Tires have strong tread remaining and are evenly worn. This is a rare opportunity to purchase a used vehicle that truly looks and drives like new. Serious buyers are encouraged to arrange an inspection \u2014 we are confident it will exceed expectations.",
      "price": 47000.0,
