    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly exceptional, mint condition \u2014 one of the finest examples you'll find on the used market. The exterior is virtually flawless, with no scratches, dents, or paint imperfections to speak of; the finish retains a deep, showroom-quality shine throughout. All body panels are perfectly aligned, and the chrome and trim pieces are spotless. The interior is immaculate \u2014 every surface, seat, and panel looks and feels as though it has barely been touched. Upholstery shows no wear, fading, or staining, and all controls, screens, and features function exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is clean and well-maintained, with full service records available. Mechanically, this car drives as smoothly and responsively as the day it left the dealership. Tires have excellent tread remaining, brakes are in great shape, and there are no warning lights or known issues. If you're looking for a used vehicle that truly feels new, this is a rare opportunity.",
      "price": 47000.0,
