    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and represents a solid, dependable used car purchase. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 paint retains a reasonable shine with only minor surface scratches and light wear consistent with normal use. There are no significant dents or structural concerns, though a close inspection will reveal the small imperfections you'd expect from a car that has been driven regularly. The interior is clean and functional, with moderate wear on high-contact surfaces like the driver's seat and steering wheel, but no tears, major stains, or damage. Mechanically, the car runs well \u2014 the engine starts reliably, transmission shifts smoothly, and all major systems are in proper working order. We recommend a pre-purchase inspection, as we always do, but buyers can expect a vehicle that is ready for everyday use without immediate major repairs needed. This is an honest, straightforward used car at a fair price.",
